{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"29b8109d38","title":"祝贺陶里亚蒂六十寿辰的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"db4a713da5","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":25,"articleId":"29b8109d38"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"870077c3e4","type":"title","text":"祝贺陶里亚蒂六十寿辰的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"bd454d8f30","type":"paragraph","text":"意大利共产党中央委员会总书记亲爱的陶里亚蒂同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"d1a77892f6","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会和我个人，在你六十寿辰之际，谨向你和意大利共产党中央委员会致最热烈的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"30df922841","type":"paragraph","text":"从你青年时代起，你就把你的全部生命贡献给意大利劳动人民的解放事业。依靠你的英勇的奋斗和卓越的领导，意大利共产党已经成为意大利工人阶级的光荣旗帜，成为意大利强大的政治力量，成为全世界马克思列宁主义的伟大堡垒之一。你对于意大利革命事业、国际工人运动和世界和平运动的光辉的贡献，使你不仅受到意大利人民、而且受到中国和世界各国人民的敬爱。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"ed84bf15b5","type":"paragraph","text":"为了意大利从美带国主义及其走狗压追下获得解放的事业的胜利，为了以苏联为首的世界和平事业和进步事业的胜利，敬祝你健康和长寿！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"5f7a065c8c","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"},{"id":"9cdeeac711","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年三月二十五日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38"}],"page":{"id":"cdac34a10c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"29b8109d38","start":102,"end":102}}}},"__N_SSG":true}